ygData.messageBody:
Ahem. Some people zone much faster than others. If I count correctly, from West
Freeport to Qeynos Hills requires passing 9 to 12 zone barriers. At two minutes
per, your 20 minutes does not leave a whole lot of time for running...

Kenross Cantoforjado, level 27 Bard, Innorruuk
(who will often be the last into a new zone even when he is the first to leave
the old one)
(this happens so often that my friends tell me to zone well before they are ready
to do so)


Naeeldar wrote:

> From: "Naeeldar" <jackal@...>
>
> Why would the trip from Qeynos to Freeport take 45 minutes? With selo's you
> can easily make it in 20.
>
> Naeeldar
